---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import AirportMap from '../components/AirportMap.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  pageKey="airport"
  title="Prevoz do aerodroma Banja Luka – Autobus, taksi, cijene | BNX"
  description="Kako doći do Aerodroma Banja Luka (BNX). Shuttle autobus 10 KM, 23 km od centra, 25–45 min vožnje. Cijene transfera, polasci, taksi alternative, parking i mapa."
  canonicalUrl="https://blprevoz.com/airport/"
>
  <!-- Airport Overview -->
  <section class="section" id="airport-overview">
    <div class="container">
      <h1 class="section__title" id="airport-title">
        <span data-lang="bhs">Prevoz do Aerodroma Banja Luka</span>
        <span data-lang="en" style="display:none">Getting to Banja Luka Airport</span>
      </h1>
      <p class="airport-intro" id="airport-intro">
        <span data-lang="bhs">
          Međunarodni aerodrom Banja Luka (IATA: BNX) nalazi se u Mahovljanima, oko 23 km
          sjeverno od centra grada. Aerodrom je povezan sa gradom shuttle autobusom kompanije
          Smiljić, a dostupne su i taksi usluge. Ispod su sve informacije potrebne za
          planiranje vašeg dolaska ili odlaska.
        </span>
        <span data-lang="en" style="display:none">
          Banja Luka International Airport (IATA: BNX) is located in Mahovljani, approximately
          23 km north of the city center. The airport is connected to the city by Smiljić
          shuttle bus, and taxi services are also available. Below you'll find all the
          information you need to plan your arrival or departure.
        </span>
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Quick Facts -->
  <section class="section airport-quickfacts" id="airport-quickfacts">
    <div class="container">
      <h2 class="section__title airport-section-title">
        <span data-lang="bhs">Osnovne informacije</span>
        <span data-lang="en" style="display:none">Quick Facts</span>
      </h2>
      <div class="quickfacts-grid">
        <div class="quickfact-card">
          <div class="quickfact-card__icon" aria-hidden="true">
            <i class="fa-solid fa-road"></i>
          </div>
          <div class="quickfact-card__label">
            <span data-lang="bhs">Udaljenost</span>
            <span data-lang="en" style="display:none">Distance</span>
          </div>
          <div class="quickfact-card__value">23 km</div>
        </div>
        <div class="quickfact-card">
          <div class="quickfact-card__icon" aria-hidden="true">
            <i class="fa-solid fa-clock"></i>
          </div>
          <div class="quickfact-card__label">
            <span data-lang="bhs">Vrijeme vožnje</span>
            <span data-lang="en" style="display:none">Travel time</span>
          </div>
          <div class="quickfact-card__value">25–45 min</div>
        </div>
        <div class="quickfact-card">
          <div class="quickfact-card__icon" aria-hidden="true">
            <i class="fa-solid fa-money-bill-wave"></i>
          </div>
          <div class="quickfact-card__label">
            <span data-lang="bhs">Cijena autobusa</span>
            <span data-lang="en" style="display:none">Bus price</span>
          </div>
          <div class="quickfact-card__value">~10 KM</div>
        </div>
        <div class="quickfact-card">
          <div class="quickfact-card__icon" aria-hidden="true">
            <i class="fa-solid fa-building"></i>
          </div>
          <div class="quickfact-card__label">
            <span data-lang="bhs">Prevoznik</span>
            <span data-lang="en" style="display:none">Operator</span>
          </div>
          <div class="quickfact-card__value">Smiljić</div>
        </div>
        <div class="quickfact-card">
          <div class="quickfact-card__icon" aria-hidden="true">
            <i class="fa-solid fa-calendar-day"></i>
          </div>
          <div class="quickfact-card__label">
            <span data-lang="bhs">Učestalost</span>
            <span data-lang="en" style="display:none">Frequency</span>
          </div>
          <div class="quickfact-card__value">
            <span data-lang="bhs">Nekoliko polazaka dnevno</span>
            <span data-lang="en" style="display:none">Few departures per day</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Shuttle Bus + Map -->
  <section class="section section--wide" id="airport">
    <div class="container">
      <h2 class="section__title airport-section-title" id="airport-shuttle-title">
        <span data-lang="bhs">Aerodromski shuttle autobus</span>
        <span data-lang="en" style="display:none">Airport Shuttle Bus</span>
      </h2>
      <AirportMap />
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Taxi Alternatives -->
  <section class="section" id="airport-taxi">
    <div class="container">
      <h2 class="section__title airport-section-title">
        <span data-lang="bhs">Taksi do aerodroma</span>
        <span data-lang="en" style="display:none">Taxi to the Airport</span>
      </h2>
      <div class="airport-content-block">
        <p>
          <span data-lang="bhs">
            Ako vam shuttle raspored ne odgovara, taksi je najjednostavnija alternativa.
            Vožnja od centra Banje Luke do aerodroma traje 20–30 minuta i košta otprilike
            40–60 KM, zavisno od prevoznika i doba dana. Preporučujemo da unaprijed
            dogovorite cijenu ili koristite aplikacije za naručivanje taksija.
          </span>
          <span data-lang="en" style="display:none">
            If the shuttle schedule doesn't work for you, a taxi is the simplest alternative.
            The ride from downtown Banja Luka to the airport takes 20–30 minutes and costs
            approximately 40–60 KM, depending on the provider and time of day. We recommend
            agreeing on the fare in advance or using taxi booking apps.
          </span>
        </p>
        <div class="airport-tip">
          <i class="fa-solid fa-lightbulb" aria-hidden="true"></i>
          <p>
            <span data-lang="bhs">
              <strong>Savjet:</strong> Mnogi hoteli u Banjoj Luci mogu organizovati transfer
              do aerodroma za goste. Raspitajte se na recepciji prilikom prijave.
            </span>
            <span data-lang="en" style="display:none">
              <strong>Tip:</strong> Many hotels in Banja Luka can arrange airport transfers
              for guests. Ask at reception during check-in.
            </span>
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Airport Parking -->
  <section class="section" id="airport-parking">
    <div class="container">
      <h2 class="section__title airport-section-title">
        <span data-lang="bhs">Parking na aerodromu</span>
        <span data-lang="en" style="display:none">Airport Parking</span>
      </h2>
      <div class="airport-content-block">
        <p>
          <span data-lang="bhs">
            Aerodrom Banja Luka koristi automatizirani sistem naplate parkinga sa prepoznavanjem
            registarskih tablica. Plaćanje je moguće putem SMS-a, na terminalu za naplatu u
            zgradi aerodroma, ili putem <a href="#goparking">GoParking mobilne aplikacije</a>.
          </span>
          <span data-lang="en" style="display:none">
            Banja Luka Airport uses an automated parking payment system with license plate
            recognition. Payment is available via SMS, at the payment terminal inside the
            airport building, or through the <a href="#goparking">GoParking mobile app</a>.
          </span>
        </p>

        <div class="parking-prices">
          <h3 class="parking-prices__title">
            <i class="fa-solid fa-square-parking" aria-hidden="true"></i>
            <span data-lang="bhs">Cjenovnik parkinga</span>
            <span data-lang="en" style="display:none">Parking Prices</span>
          </h3>
          <div class="parking-prices__grid">
            <div class="parking-price-item">
              <span class="parking-price-item__label">
                <span data-lang="bhs">Prvi sat</span>
                <span data-lang="en" style="display:none">First hour</span>
              </span>
              <span class="parking-price-item__value">3 KM</span>
            </div>
            <div class="parking-price-item">
              <span class="parking-price-item__label">
                <span data-lang="bhs">Prvih 24 sata</span>
                <span data-lang="en" style="display:none">First 24 hours</span>
              </span>
              <span class="parking-price-item__value">5 KM</span>
            </div>
            <div class="parking-price-item">
              <span class="parking-price-item__label">
                <span data-lang="bhs">Svaki sljedeći započeti dan</span>
                <span data-lang="en" style="display:none">Each subsequent started day</span>
              </span>
              <span class="parking-price-item__value">5 KM</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="airport-tip">
          <i class="fa-solid fa-circle-info" aria-hidden="true"></i>
          <p>
            <span data-lang="bhs">
              Detaljan cjenovnik parking usluga dostupan je na
              <a href="https://bnx.aero/en/home/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">službenoj stranici aerodroma</a>.
            </span>
            <span data-lang="en" style="display:none">
              A detailed parking price list is available on the
              <a href="https://bnx.aero/en/home/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">official airport website</a>.
            </span>
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="goparking-box" id="goparking">
          <div class="goparking-box__header">
            <i class="fa-solid fa-mobile-screen-button" aria-hidden="true"></i>
            <h3>
              <span data-lang="bhs">Platite parking putem GoParking aplikacije</span>
              <span data-lang="en" style="display:none">Pay for parking via GoParking app</span>
            </h3>
          </div>
          <p>
            <span data-lang="bhs">
              Skenirajte QR kod sa tiketa ili unesite broj karte, izaberite način plaćanja
              (SMS ili bankovna kartica) – jednostavno, brzo i sigurno.
            </span>
            <span data-lang="en" style="display:none">
              Scan the QR code from your ticket or enter the card number, choose payment method
              (SMS or bank card) – simple, fast and secure.
            </span>
          </p>
          <div class="goparking-box__stores">
            <a
              href="https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.goparking.airport&hl=en"
              target="_blank"
              rel="noopener noreferrer"
              class="goparking-store-badge"
            >
              <i class="fa-brands fa-google-play" aria-hidden="true"></i>
              Google Play
            </a>
            <a
              href="https://apps.apple.com/ba/app/goparking-aerodromi-rs/id6746559109"
              target="_blank"
              rel="noopener noreferrer"
              class="goparking-store-badge"
            >
              <i class="fa-brands fa-apple" aria-hidden="true"></i>
              App Store
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Useful Links -->
  <section class="section" id="airport-links">
    <div class="container">
      <h2 class="section__title airport-section-title">
        <span data-lang="bhs">Korisni linkovi</span>
        <span data-lang="en" style="display:none">Useful Links</span>
      </h2>
      <div class="airport-links-grid">
        <a
          href="https://bnx.aero/en/home/"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener noreferrer"
          class="airport-link-card"
        >
          <i class="fa-solid fa-plane" aria-hidden="true"></i>
          <div>
            <strong>
              <span data-lang="bhs">Aerodrom Banja Luka</span>
              <span data-lang="en" style="display:none">Banja Luka Airport</span>
            </strong>
            <span class="airport-link-card__url">bnx.aero</span>
          </div>
          <i class="fa-solid fa-arrow-up-right-from-square airport-link-card__arrow" aria-hidden="true"></i>
        </a>
        <a
          href="https://smiljiccompany.ba/avio-transferi/"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener noreferrer"
          class="airport-link-card"
        >
          <i class="fa-solid fa-bus" aria-hidden="true"></i>
          <div>
            <strong>
              <span data-lang="bhs">Smiljić – Avio transferi</span>
              <span data-lang="en" style="display:none">Smiljić – Airport Transfers</span>
            </strong>
            <span class="airport-link-card__url">smiljiccompany.ba</span>
          </div>
          <i class="fa-solid fa-arrow-up-right-from-square airport-link-card__arrow" aria-hidden="true"></i>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
